{
  "stem": "14900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Early, early one morning, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[GERMAN] Schnell!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Schnell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were cramped from sitting like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There wasn't even a chamber pot by then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We were sitting in our own feces and urine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "People had diarrhea, dysentery, vomiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I remember at least three bodies dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "How many more in the other part of the car, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We were forced to jump down and immediately they separated the men from the women, the women and children walking one direction, men in the opposite direction.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So it was like this way, split.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Stood single file, and I saw a sign, and it was such a pretty, black rod iron gate, very ornate-- 'Arbeit macht frei.' Work makes one free.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And underneath it someplace I saw this sign, a little, like, a train city sign-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I just thought we had arrived in a town named Auschwietchem to go to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And then I heard whispers down the line, Auschwitz, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Auschwietchem, of course, as we all now know was Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "That was the town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I realized right away that they were sorting, separating us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "You had to go past their review committee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "There were three SS uniformed men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I've heard since that Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Mengele was always one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I had no idea who they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And I noticed that the elderly, young children, and women with infants were all being sent to the left.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "All the younger, stronger, able-bodied women were going to the right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Well, I was in front of my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I was still wearing the three dresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I still had the long hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Here's the ironic part of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I was too young for the labor side of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
